程序包 petclinic

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Clinic
    The high-level petclinic business interface.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ClinicImpl
    Default implementation of the Clinic interface.
    Entity
    Simple JavaBean business object with an id property.
    NamedEntity
    Simple JavaBean business object adds a name property to Entity.
    Owner
    Simple JavaBean business object representing an owner.
    Person
    Simple JavaBean business object representing an person.
    Pet
    Simple JavaBean business object representing a pet.
    Vet
    Simple JavaBean business object representing a veterinarian.
    Visit
    Simple JavaBean business object representing a visit.
  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    NoSuchEntityException
    Exception thrown when an id reference is made to an Entity that should be in the system but is not.
